public class Document
extends VAnnotation
This is a container class for a document and header. A document contains a document body (a set of annotations), and a document header that contains meta-data about the document. Updated by JCasGen Wed Aug 17 13:31:49 EDT 2022 XML source: C:/Users/divitag2/work/softwareRepos/bodyFunction/project/60_03_type-descriptors/target/jcasgen/typesystem.xml
